      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error beyond discretization error is not required to be separately assessed at Model Risk Level 2 for this COU. The discretization error assessment provides sufficient numerical credibility evidence."
    },
    {
