    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Predicted RH indices agree with experimental measurements within the 15% acceptance criterion at all five operating points. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 given the medium model influence and existing experimental confirmation of results.",
